    "I returned early" : "Jeg kom tidligt kvar",
    "I understand this action cannot be undone" : "Jeg forst\u00e5r, at denne \u00e5tg\u00e4rd inte kan fortrydes",
    "If a break is left open for too long, the system automatically clocks out to prevent permanent pause status." : "Hvis en rast st\u00e5r \u00e5ben f\u00f6r l\u00e6nge, stemper systemet automatisk ud f\u00f6r at undg\u00e5 permanent raststatus.",
    "If a calendar month was finalized by mistake or a correction is required, you can reopen it here as an administrator for the employee whose month should be opened again. Use the search field to select that person (their Nextcloud account). You must enter a reason; the audit log records your administrator action, the reason, and who the change applies to. Previous snapshot rows remain in the database for traceability." : "Hvis en kalenderm\u00e5ned er afsluttet ved en fejl, eller som er behov f\u00f6r en rettelse, kan du gen\u00e5bne den her som administrator f\u00f6r den medarbetare, hvis m\u00e5ned skal \u00e5bnes igen. Brug s\u00f8gefeltet till at v\u00e6lge denne person (deres Nextcloud-konto). Du skal indtaste en orsak; revisionsloggen registrerer din administrator\u00e5tg\u00e4rd, orsaken och hvem \u00e6ndringen g\u00e6lsom for. Tidligere snapshot-r\u00e6kker forbliver i databasen f\u00f6r sporbarhed.",
    "If enabled, users can still turn this reminder off in their personal settings. Reminders are sent only for expected workdays (not weekends, holidays, or approved absences)." : "Hvis den er aktiveret, kan anv\u00e4ndare stadig sl\u00e5 denne p\u00e5mindelse fr\u00e5n i deres personlige inst\u00e4llningar. P\u00e5mindelser sendes kun f\u00f6r forventede arbetsdagar (ikke weekender, helgdagar eller godk\u00e4nd fr\u00e5nvaro).",
    "If enabled: managers are resolved from ArbeitszeitCheck teams defined below. If disabled: managers are resolved from shared Nextcloud groups (default behavior)." : "Hvis aktiveret: chefer l\u00f8ses fr\u00e5n ArbeitszeitCheck-teams defineret nedenfor. Hvis deaktiveret: chefer l\u00f8ses fr\u00e5n delte Nextcloud-grupper (standardadf\u00e6rd).",
    "If set, opening carryover per user cannot exceed this many days (Tarifvertrag / company policy). Leave empty for no cap. Imports and admin edits are clamped to this value." : "Hvis det er indstillet, kan \u00e5bningsoverf\u00f8rsel pr. bruger inte overstige s\u00e5 mange dagar (Tarifvertrag / f\u00f6retagspolitik). Lad v\u00e6re tom f\u00f6r ingen l\u00e5g. Importer och administratorredigeringer er fastgjort till denne v\u00e6rdi.",
    "If set, this date is saved as the overtime \u201cStichtag\u201d when the new account is created. Leave empty to configure later in ArbeitszeitCheck \u2192 Administration \u2192 Employees." : "Hvis den er angivet, gemmes denne dato som \u00f6vertidt \"Stichtag\", n\u00e5r den nye konto oprettes. Lad v\u00e6re tom f\u00f6r at konfigurere senere i ArbeitszeitCheck \u2192 Administration \u2192 Medarbetaree.",
    "If you manage more than one team, you can choose one here." : "Hvis du chef mer end \u00e9t team, kan du v\u00e6lge et her.",
    "If you need help at any time, check the documentation or contact your administrator." : "Hvis du till enhver tid har brug f\u00f6r hj\u00e6lp, kan du kontrollerake dokumentationen eller kontakte din administrator.",
    "If you need to generate reports, please contact your administrator or manager." : "Hvis du har brug f\u00f6r at generere rapporter, bedes du kontakte din administrator eller chef.",
    "If you think the result is wrong, please contact your HR administrator." : "Hvis du mener, at resultatet er forkert, bedes du kontakte din HR-administrator.",
    "If you were sick during vacation, please shorten or cancel the vacation first, then submit a separate sick leave request." : "Hvis du har v\u00e6ret syg i semestern, bedes du f\u00f8rst afkorte eller aflyse semestern och derefter indsende en s\u00e6rskilt sygemeldingsbeg\u00e4ran.",
