    "Opening balance hours must be a number between -9999 and 9999." : "\u00c5bningssaldotimmar skal v\u00e6re et tal mellem -9999 och 9999.",
    "Opening balance of carryover days for the selected calendar year (Resturlaub), e.g. from HR or migration. This is not the annual vacation entitlement from the working time model. The last day carryover can be used is set globally in Admin settings." : "\u00c5bningssaldo f\u00f6r overf\u00f8rselsdagar f\u00f6r det valgte kalender\u00e5r (Resturlaub), t.ex. fr\u00e5n HR eller migration. Dette er inte den \u00e5rlige semesterret fr\u00e5n arbetstidsmodelllen. Den sidste dag, overf\u00f8rsel kan bruges, indstilles globalt i administratorinst\u00e4llningar.",
