    "Optional: Add notes or details about this work period (e.g., project work, meetings, tasks)" : "Valgfrit: L\u00e4gg till noter eller detaljer om denne arbejdsperiode (t.ex. projektarbejde, m\u00f8der, opgaver)",
    "Optional: Record your break times. Breaks of at least 15 minutes count toward legal requirements (ArbZG \u00a74)." : "Valgfrit: Registrer dina rasttider. Rastr p\u00e5 mindst 15 minuter t\u00e6ller med i lovkrav (ArbZG \u00a74).",
    "Optional: Record your break times. Breaks of at least 15 minutes count toward legal requirements (ArbZG \u00a74). You can add multiple breaks." : "Valgfrit: Registrer dina rasttider. Rastr p\u00e5 mindst 15 minuter t\u00e6ller med i lovkrav (ArbZG \u00a74). Du kan l\u00e4gg tille flere raster.",
    "Optional: Record your break times. German law requires breaks for work over 6 hours: 30 minutes for 6-9 hours, 45 minutes for 9+ hours. Shorter shifts have no break requirements. Automatic breaks are added when needed for compliance. You can add additional manual breaks." : "Valgfrit: Registrer dina rasttider. Tysk lov kr\u00e6ver raster f\u00f6r arbejde over 6 timmar: 30 minuter f\u00f6r 6-9 timmar, 45 minuter f\u00f6r 9+ timmar. Kortere vagter har ingen rastkrav. Automatiske raster l\u00e4gg tilles, n\u00e5r det er n\u00f8dvendigt f\u00f6r overteamelse. Du kan l\u00e4gg tille ytterligare manuelle raster.",
