    "Total:%1$d, Working:%2$d, Break:%3$d, Paused:%4$d, Clocked out:%5$d. Absent:%6$d (Vacation:%7$d, Sick:%8$d, Other:%9$d)." : "I alt:%1$d, Arbejder:%2$d, Rast:%3$d, Rast:%4$d, Tidsbegr\u00e6nset:%5$d. Fr\u00e5nvaroende:%6$d (Semester:%7$d, Syg:%8$d, Andet:%9$d).",
