    "Upper bound: counts users without an L1/L2/L3 override at all. Some users may still be served by a higher layer." : "\u00d8vre gr\u00e6nse: t\u00e6ller anv\u00e4ndare uden en L1/L2/L3-tilsides\u00e6ttelse overhovedet. Nogle anv\u00e4ndare kan stadig betjenes av et h\u00f8jere lag.",
    "Upper limit of daily working time in hours. German labor law (ArbZG) allows 8 hours normally, up to 10 in special cases." : "\u00d8vre gr\u00e6nse f\u00f6r daglig arbejdstid i timmar. Tysk arbejdslovgivning (ArbZG) tillasom normalt 8 timmar, op till 10 i s\u00e6rlige tilf\u00e6lde.",
    "Use \"Start Break\" and \"End Break\" to record your breaks. The system will remind you if you forget." : "Brug \"Start rast\" och \"Afslut rast\" till at optage dina raster. Systemet vil minde dig om, hvis du glemmer det.",
    "Use 0\u2013366 in steps of 0.5 (for example 25 or 25.5)." : "Brug 0\u2013366 i trin p\u00e5 0,5 (for eksempel 25 eller 25,5).",
    "Use ArbeitszeitCheck teams for approvals" : "Brug ArbeitszeitCheck-teams till godk\u00e4nnelser",
    "Use ArbeitszeitCheck teams instead of Nextcloud groups" : "Brug ArbeitszeitCheck-team i stedet f\u00f6r Nextcloud-grupper",
    "Use app teams setting saved" : "Brug app teams indstilling gemt",
    "Use fixed value, automatic from schedule, or tariff rule. Exception mode requires a reason." : "Brug fast v\u00e6rdi, automatisk fr\u00e5n tidsplan eller tarifregel. Undtagelsestilstand kr\u00e6ver en grund.",
    "Use global default state" : "Brug global standardtilstand",
    "Use quick actions and role-based status sections in one place." : "Brug hurtige \u00e5tg\u00e4rsom och rollebaserede statussektioner p\u00e5 \u00e9t sted.",
    "Use the \"Clock In\" button to start tracking your work time. When you finish, click \"Clock Out\" to stop." : "Brug knappen \"Stem ind\" f\u00f6r at begynde at spore din arbejdstid. N\u00e5r du er f\u00e6rdig, skal du klikke p\u00e5 \"Stem ud\" f\u00f6r at stoppe.",
    "Use the same form for old vacation, sick leave, migration records, and future requests. Closed months stay protected and cannot be changed unless an administrator reopens them." : "Brug den samme formular till gamle semester-, sygeorlovs-, migrationsregistre och fremtidige beg\u00e4raner. Lukkede m\u00e5nesom forbliver beskyttet och kan inte \u00e6ndres, medmindre en administrator gen\u00e5bner dem.",
    "Use these buttons to track your working hours. Click \"Clock In\" when you start working and \"Clock Out\" when you finish." : "Brug disse knapper till at spore din arbejdstid. Klik p\u00e5 \"Stem ind\", n\u00e5r du begynsom at arbejde, och \"Stem ud\", n\u00e5r du er f\u00e6rdig.",
    "Use this form to edit your time entry. The form will automatically check compliance with German labor law requirements." : "Brug denne formular till at redigere din tidsregistrering. Formularen vil automatisk kontrollere overteamelse av tysk arbejdsretlige krav.",
    "Use this form to record when you worked. Fill in the date, start time, end time, and optionally break times. The form will automatically check compliance with German labor law requirements." : "Brug denne formular till at registrere, hvorn\u00e5r du arbetade. Udfyld dato, starttidspunkt, sluttidspunkt och eventuelt rasttider. Formularen vil automatisk kontrollere overteamelse av tysk arbejdsretlige krav.",
    "Use valid email addresses separated by commas. Duplicates are removed automatically." : "Brug gyldige e-postadresser adskilt av kommaer. Dubletter ta bortes automatisk.",
    "Used for statutory holidays and compliance when no specific state is configured for employees or teams." : "Bruges till lagstadgade helgdagar och overteamelse, n\u00e5r som inte er konfigureret nogen specifik tilstand f\u00f6r medarbetare eller teams.",
    "Used this year" : "Brugt i \u00e5r",
