    "When ProjectCheck is enabled, you can optionally link billing hours on a project the employee is allowed to use." : "N\u00e5r ProjectCheck er aktiveret, kan du valfrit sammenk\u00e6de faktureringstimmar p\u00e5 et projekt, medarbetaren m\u00e5 bruge.",
