    "When a substitute is selected, emails can be sent at each step of the approval process." : "N\u00e5r en vikarie er valgt, kan e-posts sendes p\u00e5 hvert trin i godk\u00e4nnelsesprocessen.",
    "When an absence is approved, the employee can receive an email with an iCalendar (.ics) attachment so they can add the absence to their calendar." : "N\u00e5r et fr\u00e5nvaro er godk\u00e4nd, kan medarbetaren modtage en e-post med en iCalendar (.ics) bifogad fil, s\u00e5 de kan l\u00e4gg tille fr\u00e5nvaroet till deres kalender.",
